modules.description: Represents source code positions with filename, line, column, and offset. Provides a pretty-printing function to format these positions and a logging tag definition for structured logging. Useful for tracking and displaying locations in source code during error reporting or debugging.

Handles source code position tracking with structured representation of file locations, including line and column numbers. Provides pretty-printing for these positions and integrates with logging systems to annotate events with source context. Useful for precise error diagnostics and source mapping in tools like linters or compilers.
